name: Universe #260
description: Universe #260 - The dark universe Chinuvis was a violent one. It attacked other universes all over the void and carried their colors in it's cracks as trophies. 260 was disturbed by all this violence as it tried to stop it. The blackness and the colored spoils of all the destroyed universes imprinted on it. Yet it stopped and now travels with 260 in a forever angry state, stopped but disturbed forever.
